channel.title: Need some more help: Port forwarding trouble
channel.description: Well, I fixed my other problem (thanks to those of you who helped). I ran into another one during port forwarding. I found my default gateway, and I type it into the the webpage and a thing pops up that asks me if I want to connect to my gateway, and asks me for a username and password... what is my username and password? I've never done this before, how do I find out what that is?
